%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fc31e614b1789304f9899d89689c7c54, type: 3}
  m_Name: Narrative_WakeUp
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::_Scripts.Tutorial.TutorialNarrativeAsset
  beats:
  - speaker: 0
    text: Before the Peace, there was the Fracture. A war without winners. Nations
      dissolving into each other like wet paper, taking everything they had built
      with them.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: Father Mark did not look away.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 3
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: 'While others mourned, he rebuilt. What remained of Earth''s governing
      bodies consolidated under one name: AGEU. Under one vision. Under one man.'
    autoAdvanceDelay: 5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: The Fracture ended. Not with a treaty. With leadership.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 4
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: But peace is expensive. A recovered Earth is hungry. And Father Mark had
      never once failed to find an answer.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 4.5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: He found many through well kept relations with other planets. Deep. Far
      and quiet civillisations.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 4
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: The facilities were built. The work began. And for the first time in living
      memory, our Earth strived.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 3
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: You are part of that work.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 3
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: Darkness. Then pressure. Then the dull ache of a floor that has been your
      bed for longer than it should have been.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 4.5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: You don't know where you are. You don't know how you got here.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 3.5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
  - speaker: 0
    text: Get up anyway.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 2
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    keepHologramActive: 0
